<TITLE> Private universities to remain open </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Aug 25 (bdnews24.com) -- Private universities and all other educational institutions except for public universities and government and private colleges in divisional cities would remain open, the government said in a statement Saturday. The statement said the authorities of graduate colleges outside the divisional cities could make decisions on their ownto keep their institutions open or otherwiseconsidering the situation. The government closed all public universities and government and private colleges in divisional cities after law and order spiralled out of control in the wake of Dhaka University violence on the night of August 20. bd
